{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be sleek and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sleek Designs</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0a2342; /* Deep blue */\n            --secondary-color: #243b55; /* Slightly lighter blue */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --accent-color: #e0e0e0;\n            --hover-color: #1d4d7e;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 10;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            letter-spacing: 3px;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--hover-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            border-color: var(--hover-color);\n        }\n\n        .services {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .services h3 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .portfolio {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio h3 {\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item {\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 250px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            display: block;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-overlay {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background-color: rgba(10, 35, 66, 0.8); /* Primary color with transparency */\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            opacity: 0;\n            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-item:hover .portfolio-overlay {\n            opacity: 1;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-overlay h4 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .portfolio-overlay p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Simple animation for hero text */\n        @keyframes fadeInUp {\n            from {\n                opacity: 0;\n                transform: translateY(20px);\n            }\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .hero h2, .hero p {\n            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }\n        .hero p { animation-delay: 0.5s; }\n        .cta-button { animation-delay: 0.8s; }\n\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons (optional, but good for services) -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Sleek Designs</h1>\n            <p>Crafting Digital Experiences</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Transform Your Vision into Reality</h2>\n            <p>We offer cutting-edge design solutions to elevate your brand.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get a Quote</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Services</h3>\n            <div class=\"service-grid\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-paint-brush\"></i>\n                    <h4>Web Design</h4>\n                    <p>Creating intuitive and visually stunning websites that engage your audience.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-mobile-alt\"></i>\n                    <h4>App Design</h4>\n                    <p>Seamless user experiences for mobile applications across all platforms.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-vector-square\"></i>\n                    <h4>Branding</h4>\n                    <p>Developing strong brand identities that resonate with your target market.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                    <h4>UI/UX Consulting</h4>\n                    <p>Expert guidance to optimize user interfaces and improve overall usability.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"portfolio\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Work</h3>\n            <div class=\"portfolio-grid\">\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/0a2342/ffffff?text=Project+One\" alt=\"Project One\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-overlay\">\n                        <h4>Project One</h4>\n                        <p>E-commerce Platform</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/243b55/ffffff?text=Project+Two\" alt=\"Project Two\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-overlay\">\n                        <h4>Project Two</h4>\n                        <p>Mobile App UI</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/0a2342/ffffff?text=Project+Three\" alt=\"Project Three\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-overlay\">\n                        <h4>Project Three</h4>\n                        <p>Brand Identity</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"portfolio-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/243b55/ffffff?text=Project+Four\" alt=\"Project Four\">\n                    <div class=\"portfolio-overlay\">\n                        <h4>Project Four</h4>\n                        <p>SaaS Dashboard</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\" id=\"contact\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--secondary-color) 0%, var(--primary-color) 100%); padding: 60px 0;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;\">Let's Create Something Amazing</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.3em;\">Have a project in mind? Get in touch with us.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@sleekdesigns.com\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Us</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Sleek Designs. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple JS for potential future enhancements, e.g., smooth scrolling\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}